TopicTitle: Two question about locations on the Mun

Articles.Content:
I have found all the locations and biomes on Mun and Minums except 2. 
Mun Mound discoverable who is supposed to be located at (x: 34.93, y: -28.48) = north 34:56, west 28.29, the Mun or burst was at (x: -13.4, y: -69.94) = south 13:24 west 69:56 
So either the wiki is wrong or I do something wrong. Yes it took some time for me to realize that micro engineer used minutes and second not decimal for location. 
Or is it just hard to differentiate from other rocks? 

Mare Eye I have no idea about and google shows has just junk about kerbal eyes.
